<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1005226>
    dc:description "FIGURES 15 – 21. Ruppeliana longiphallus sp. nov. 15, male holotype (total length 9.7 mm), dorsal view (antennae and legs not depicted), MNRJ. Male genitalia: 16, pygofer, valve, and subgenital plate, lateral view; 17, valve and subgenital plate, ventral view; 18, connective and style, dorsal view; 19, aedeagus, lateral view; 20, aedeagus, ventral view. 21, female sternite VII, ventral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1005226/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1005222>
    dc:description "FIGURES 8 – 14. Ruppeliana grossii sp. nov. 8, male holotype (total length 8.8 mm), dorsal view (antennae and legs not depicted), MNRJ. Male genitalia: 9, pygofer, valve, and subgenital plate, lateral view; 10, valve and subgenital plate, ventral view; 11, connective and style, dorsal view; 12, aedeagus, lateral view; 13, aedeagus, ventral view. 14, female sternite VII, ventral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1005222/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1005220>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 7. Ruppeliana barbarensis sp. nov. 1, female paratype (total length 10.3 mm), dorsal view (antennae and legs not depicted), DZUP. Male genitalia: 2, pygofer, valve, and subgenital plate, lateral view; 3, valve and subgenital plates, ventral view; 4, connective and style, dorsal view; 5, aedeagus, lateral view; 6, aedeagus, ventral view. 7, female sternite VII, ventral view." ;
